<!--
  Skip Link: An accessibility feature for keyboard users.

  When you press Tab on a page, this is the first thing that gets focus.
  It lets you jump straight to the main content, skipping the navigation.
  Sighted mouse users never see it (it's off-screen until focused).
  Screen reader users hear it announced immediately.

  The href="#main-content" points to the <main id="main-content"> element
  in the layout.
-->
<a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">
  Skip to main content
</a>
